    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the vegetables have slightly softened, add your <strong>vegetable stock mix</strong> and 2 tbsp<span class=\"text-purple\"> [3 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp] </span><strong>cold water</strong></p><p>Add your <strong>Henderson's Relish </strong>and <strong>half </strong>your <strong>onion marmalade </strong>(you'll use the rest later!) and give everything a good mix up</p><p>Cook, covered, for a further 1-2 min or until the vegetables are tender – this is your<strong> pasty filling</strong></p>",
