    {
      "instruction": "<p>Dust your work surface with a generous sprinkling of <strong>flour</strong></p><p>Unwrap your<strong> pastry</strong> and roll it out to approx. 0.5cm thickness with a <strong>rolling pin </strong>and cut into 1 square per person</p><p>Line a baking tray (or two!) with <strong>non-stick baking paper </strong>and add the <strong>pastry square[s]</strong></p><p>Add the<strong> pasty filling</strong> to one corner of the <strong>pastry square[s] </strong>and fold the corner over to make a triangle shape</p>",
